                "id": "ex-2025-05-09-1",
                "chapter": "数列(临时)",
                "difficulty": 2,
                "body": "设 $a_n = 2^n - 1$,求 $\\displaystyle\\sum_{i=1}^{5} a_i$ 的值。",
                "solution": [
                    "$\\displaystyle\\sum_{i=1}^{5}(2^i - 1) = (2+4+8+16+32) - 5 = 62 - 5 = 57$。"
                ]
            },
            {
                "id": "ex-2025-05-09-2",
                "chapter": "概率统计(临时)",
                "difficulty": 1,
                "body": "袋中有 3 个白球、2 个黑球,从中任取 2 个,求两球颜色相同的概率。",
                "solution": [
                    "总取法 $\\dbinom{5}{2} = 10$。",
                    "两白:$\\dbinom{3}{2} = 3$;两黑:$\\dbinom{2}{2} = 1$。",
                    "故概率 $= \\dfrac{3 + 1}{10} = \\dfrac{2}{5}$。"
                ]
            }
        ]
